    {
        "content": "<p>Just a heads up that there are two common <code>rfl</code>s. </p>\n<p>One is a term and is pretty much just <code>Eq.refl</code> </p>\n<p>While the other is a tactic and is extended with extra reflexive relations (Plus it does some other work for you sometimes).</p>",
